    {
      "bookmarkId": "22717531_9_1768-1826",
      "chapterUid": 9,
      "range": "1768-1826",
      "markText": "陶寺的统治者，似乎是一群耽于享乐而不思开疆拓土的贵族。它的文明高度发达但却“不称霸”，因而没有形成“广域王权国家”。",
      "totalCount": 208,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=22717531&chapterUid=9&rangeStart=1768&rangeEnd=1826",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/2d232470715aa45b2d24bb9?chapterUid=9&rangeStart=1768&rangeEnd=1826"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "22717531_9_2563-2606",
      "chapterUid": 9,
      "range": "2563-2606",
      "markText": "“起于河东山西，成于河山之外”。山西这方神奇的黄土地，成为一波一波华夏文明潮的策源地。",
      "totalCount": 192,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=22717531&chapterUid=9&rangeStart=2563&rangeEnd=2606",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/2d232470715aa45b2d24bb9?chapterUid=9&rangeStart=2563&rangeEnd=2606"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "22717531_33_1947-1988",
      "chapterUid": 33,
      "range": "1947-1988",
      "markText": "说句略嫌悲观的话，我们永远也不可能获知当时的真相，但仍怀着最大限度迫近真相的执着。",
      "totalCount": 192,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=22717531&chapterUid=33&rangeStart=1947&rangeEnd=1988",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/2d232470715aa45b2d24bb9?chapterUid=33&rangeStart=1947&rangeEnd=1988"
    },
    {
