      "chapterUid": 4,
      "range": "806-898",
      "markText": "“革命”一词，在中国古典文献中，本来指朝代更替，如“汤武革命”（《易》）等。这里则是取其新意，也即社会政治变革，更进一步说，借用的是经典作家“一个阶级推翻另一个阶级的暴力行动”的概念。",
      "totalCount": 187,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=22717531&chapterUid=4&rangeStart=806&rangeEnd=898",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/2d232470715aa45b2d24bb9?chapterUid=4&rangeStart=806&rangeEnd=898"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "22717531_29_1504-1573",
      "chapterUid": 29,
      "range": "1504-1573",
      "markText": "四千多年前的城垣能够保存这么好，则首先要归功于现代化城市化的脚步还没有到达这里，它侥幸躲过了“人定胜天”时代的平整土地和圈地拆迁的推土机。",
      "totalCount": 182,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=22717531&chapterUid=29&rangeStart=1504&rangeEnd=1573",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/2d232470715aa45b2d24bb9?chapterUid=29&rangeStart=1504&rangeEnd=1573"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "22717531_3_965-1041",
      "chapterUid": 3,
      "range": "965-1041",
      "markText": "自“中国考古学之父”李济先生1926年发掘山西夏县西阴村，1928年中央研究院历史语言研究所发掘河南安阳殷墟以来，中国考古学参与古史建构的历史已近百年。",
      "totalCount": 176,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=22717531&chapterUid=3&rangeStart=965&rangeEnd=1041",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/2d232470715aa45b2d24bb9?chapterUid=3&rangeStart=965&rangeEnd=1041"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "22717531_14_481-659",
      "chapterUid": 14,
      "range": "481-659",
      "markText": "把一个社会崩溃的原因归结为五点因素，即生态破坏、气候变更、强邻在侧、友邦援助的减少以及社会自身应对之道，并认为最后一点是至为关键的。",
      "totalCount": 156,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=22717531&chapterUid=14&rangeStart=481&rangeEnd=659",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/2d232470715aa45b2d24bb9?chapterUid=14&rangeStart=481&rangeEnd=659"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "22717531_5_1838-1864",
      "chapterUid": 5,
      "range": "1838-1864",
      "markText": "古代中国人“事死如事生”，墓葬是生前生活环境的缩影。",
      "totalCount": 154,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=22717531&chapterUid=5&rangeStart=1838&rangeEnd=1864",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/2d232470715aa45b2d24bb9?chapterUid=5&rangeStart=1838&rangeEnd=1864"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "22717531_7_421-476",
      "chapterUid": 7,
      "range": "421-476",
      "markText": "值得注意的是，陶寺贵族墓葬所显现的这套礼仪制度，既有日后被三代王朝文明继承下来的，也有大量就此失传成为绝响的。",
      "totalCount": 153,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=22717531&chapterUid=7&rangeStart=421&rangeEnd=476",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/2d232470715aa45b2d24bb9?chapterUid=7&rangeStart=421&rangeEnd=476"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "22717531_3_1524-1708",
      "chapterUid": 3,
      "range": "1524-1708",
      "markText": "只能勾画一个轮廓，这主要是由考古学的学科特点决定的。那就是，其以长时段的、历史与文化发展进程的宏观考察见长，而对精确年代和具体历史事件的把握则不是它的强项。",
      "totalCount": 150,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=22717531&chapterUid=3&rangeStart=1524&rangeEnd=1708",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/2d232470715aa45b2d24bb9?chapterUid=3&rangeStart=1524&rangeEnd=1708"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "22717531_28_2278-2312",
      "chapterUid": 28,
      "range": "2278-2312",
      "markText": "这类推想想当然的成分太多，或者干脆已进入当代意义上的“八卦”的范畴。",
      "totalCount": 144,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=22717531&chapterUid=28&rangeStart=2278&rangeEnd=2312",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/2d232470715aa45b2d24bb9?chapterUid=28&rangeStart=2278&rangeEnd=2312"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "22717531_30_2045-2057",
      "chapterUid": 30,
      "range": "2045-2057",
      "markText": "贪欲是文明社会形成的动力",
      "totalCount": 144,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=22717531&chapterUid=30&rangeStart=2045&rangeEnd=2057",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/2d232470715aa45b2d24bb9?chapterUid=30&rangeStart=2045&rangeEnd=2057"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "22717531_3_554-633",
      "chapterUid": 3,
      "range": "554-633",
      "markText": "深入发掘“中国”之所以为“中国”的环境与文化底蕴，无疑会更全面地澄清我国统一的多民族国家形成的历史轨迹。对中国历史的长程观察有助于了解最早的“中国”何以诞生。",
      "totalCount": 136,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=22717531&chapterUid=3&rangeStart=554&rangeEnd=633",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/2d232470715aa45b2d24bb9?chapterUid=3&rangeStart=554&rangeEnd=633"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "22717531_3_2305-2368",
      "chapterUid": 3,
      "range": "2305-2368",
